01:04:37,660 --> 01:04:45,340
So it was less than 1% absolute risk increase, even if it turned out to be true, which by the

641
01:04:45,340 --> 01:04:51,980
way, to simplify matters, when I'm talking to women about the risks of hormone replacement

642
01:04:51,980 --> 01:04:57,340
therapy, I say, as a general rule, consider the Women's Health Initiative, you're ceiling on risk.

643
01:04:57,900 --> 01:05:03,020
This is probably as bad as it would get. And if you would accept that there's an increase of 1%

644
01:05:03,020 --> 01:05:07,820
in your risk of breast cancer, and here are all the caveats on why I find that hard to believe,

645
01:05:08,380 --> 01:05:13,820
but at least you have a case study here for how bad it could be when you stack the deck against

